data.description: Newly Remodeled and Close to Walker's Bluff Casino Resort! This Home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car detached garage on an acre in the country. Home has new electrical, plumbing, instant on demand hot water heater, flooring, appliances, kitchen sink and countertops. Detached 2 car garage could be used for storage or a workshop. The opportunities are endless. The rear patio is perfect for relaxing! This home is a must see! It will not last long! Make an appointment today!
